rComments: The best professor ever! He really teaches concepts very well, and his lectures are very interesting. His exams are also really fair. He's definitely one of the greatest professors at UTSC.

I think this was his first year teaching Evolutionary and it showed in the best ways. He was always enthusiastic and  really well prepared for his lectures. He's very clear and likes to keep lectures light by making jokes. His midterm was very easy but his final was much harder. Overall I enjoyed his class a lot.
